INSERT INTO `#__rsform_submission_values` (`SubmissionValueId`,`FormId`,`SubmissionId`,`FieldName`,`FieldValue`) VALUES ('','{FormId}','{SubmissionId}','Description','Hi!

Attached is screenshot.
Let me know what you could do and what it would cost in total?
Or what are easy things to do and what features would take more time?

I'd like to have menu fading away and show image without menu. 
When touched screen menu appears again.

Here's buttons I'd like to have in Main Menu.

Main Menu (bottom of screen, see screenshot)

Settings icon
- To set daily alarm/reminder, set which time of day user wants reminder.

Info icon
- Links to (external) pages: Contact Us, Suggest Images, Credits
 - Or can Contact Us open text field where user can email us?

Motivate Me (Show random image)

Share
- Facebook
 - Facebook sharing. I'd like show text on Facebook post and link to App(url) with image shared.
- Twitter
 - Link to app and custom text with image tweeted
- Email
 - Link to app and custom text on email.

More (I'd like have this button orange)
- Shows external html page which has links to other apps or
- Show Chartboost/Tapjoy app page/offer wall

SDKs to install:
- Flurry Analytics or Google Analytics
- AdWhirl for top screen ads
- Chartboost/Tapjoy for More page to show other apps

Functions in app
- When user press Home-button to exit app. I want to show Chartboost whole screen add banner.
- Possibility to send Push Notifications
 - Pre-programmed, to remind user fg. if user haven't used app for week etc.
 - Broadcast, to send notification when new images are added etc.

Let me know how this sounds and if you have any questions?

We could start with very basic app that only shows random imageâ¦

Sami' )

For some reason i just can\'t stop trying to find out what\'s going on. I hope you understand, thank you! ' )
